snippet.title: Islands of the Caliph - Official Launch Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
Islands of the Caliph is an open-world grid-based CRPG developed by Schmidt Workshops. Based on Middle Eastern folklore and Islamic spiritual tradition, players will combat enemies and seek knowledge of known regions. Collect and organize tools to sail to new lands and find resources and treasures. Islands of the Caliph is available now for PC.

#IslandsOfTheCaliph
